    <div id="main-content">

		<div id="property-intro">
		Located just steps from the Pacific Ocean and the famous fitness paths and outdoor gymnastics parks that
		run along the shore, the Loews Santa Monica Beach Hotel is one of the best luxury hotels in Santa Monica, California. 
		With the Pacific Ocean on one side and the colorful cityscape of Santa Monica on the other, the
		breezy yet elegant hotel features 45-foot palm trees inside the four-story atrum lobby and open views to the sea. 
		And guestrooms mirror the crisp sea air and the spirit of Santa Monica with breathtaking views, subtle hues and a fresh design.
		</div>
		
