		<div id="whats-new">
			<h3>What's New at Loews Santa Monica Beach Hotel!</h3>
			<p>Ocean Spa &amp; Fitness Center at Loews Santa Monica Beach Hotel introduces a tasty treatment that provides complete refreshment for the senses, the Ice Cream Pedicure. This refreshing spa pedicure features ice cream flavored bath products from MeBath! The treatment consists of a soak in a flavored bath fizz, a chocolate sherbet flavored foot scrub, and a foot mask in chocolate, marshmallow or caramel flavor followed by your choice of nail color. In addition, our Beauty and The Beach package features a customized beach workout from State of the Heart Fitness. After your workout you can invigorate your muscles with a 50-minute sports massage followed by a spa pedicure.  This package includes a one night stay in a premium room, a massage, and spa pedicure and starts at $800. Additional spa treatments and amenities are available upon request.</p>
